title: Jenkins and Jonez - Miles Bridges, New-Look 76ers, and a Conversation About Ukraine

description:
The guys discuss Hank the Tank and how to handle bears, Miles Bridges being the best rapper in NBA history, and James Harden on the 76ers before having an honest conversation about the situation in Ukraine.
